{start_of_verse: Verse 1}
[C]After yesterday you broke this heart of [F]mine
[C]You left me sad and [G7]blue
[C]Each hour I hope that you’ll be near to [F]me
[C]And hope that [G7]you’ll always be [C]true
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 2}
[F]After yesterday you broke this heart of [C]mine
[G7]Here’s what I wish that you would do
[C]Send along one of your [F]photographs
[C]Then I [G7]will always think of [C]you
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 3}
